flowchart TD
    Start([Проект с OVERVIEW/ARCHITECTURE/CLAUDE]) --> P1
    P1["/backlog"] --> A1[backlog-planner: эпики E-001, E-002]
    A1 --> BL[(.task/backlog.md)]
    BL --> Pick{Выбрать эпик}
    Pick --> P2["/plan E-001"]
    P2 --> A2[epic-planner: подзадачи, DAG, волны, риски, DoD]
    A2 --> PL[(.task/plan-E-001.md)]
    A2 --> BL2[(backlog.md: E-001 In Progress)]
    BL2 --> P3["/execute E-001"]
    P3 --> EX[создаёт feat/E-001 от main]
    EX --> W1[Волна 1: N execution-agent в worktree]
    W1 --> R1[release-manager merge: волна → feat/E-001]
    R1 --> W2[Волна 2]
    W2 --> Wn[...]
    Wn --> REP[(.task/report-E-001.md)]
    REP --> Dlg[Диалог внутри /execute]
    Dlg -->|принять| P4["/release E-001"]
    Dlg -->|доработать| P3
    Dlg -->|откатить| Abort[удалить feat/E-001]
    P4 --> REL[release-manager full: feat/E-001 → main, CHANGELOG, tag]
    REL --> Done([Эпик закрыт])
    Done --> Pick
